-- Al-Qaeda May Have Blown Up Oil Pipeline in Southern Yemen, Arabiya Reports
-- B y   M a s s o u d   A .   D e r h a l l y
-- 2010-11-02T13:22:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/al-qaeda-may-have-blown-up-oil-pipeline-in-southern-yemen-arabiya-reports.html
Al-Qaeda may have been behind the oil
pipeline explosion in southern Yemen today, Dubai-based Al-
Arabiya channel reported, citing an unidentified Yemeni
official.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Massoud A. Derhally  in Beirut, Lebanon at   mderhally@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Peter Hirschberg at  phirschberg@bloomberg.net . 